flowchart LR
    Start[Start] --> Introduce_and_Consent[Introduce and Take Consent]
    Introduce_and_Consent --> Position_Patient[Position the Patient]
    Position_Patient --> Inspection_Side[Inspect from Side of Bed]
    Inspection_Side --> Inspection_Foot[Inspect from Foot of Bed]
    Inspection_Foot --> Hair[Hair Examination]
    Hair --> Eyebrows[Eyebrows Examination]
    Eyebrows --> Eyes[Eyes Examination]
    Eyes --> Nose[Nose Examination]
    Nose --> Mouth[Mouth Examination]
    Mouth --> Lymph_Nodes[Lymph Nodes Examination]
    Lymph_Nodes --> Hands[Hands Examination]
    Hands --> Fingernails[Fingernails Examination]
    Fingernails --> Legs[Legs Examination]
    Legs --> Thank_Patient[Thank the Patient]

    // Findings for Hair
    Hair --> Fluffy[Fluffy]
    Fluffy --> Hypoalbuminemia[Hypoalbuminemia]
    Hypoalbuminemia --> Serum_Albumin[Serum Albumin]
    Fluffy --> Malnutrition[Malnutrition]
    Malnutrition --> Nutritional_Assessment[Nutritional Assessment]
    Hair --> Alopecia[Alopecia]
    Alopecia --> Patchy[Patchy]
    Patchy --> Alopecia_Areata[Alopecia Areata]
    Alopecia_Areata --> Scalp_Examination[Scalp Examination]
    Patchy --> Tinea_Capitis[Tinea Capitis]
    Tinea_Capitis --> Fungal_Culture[Fungal Culture]
    Alopecia --> Diffuse[Diffuse]
    Diffuse --> Telogen_Effluvium[Telogen Effluvium]
    Telogen_Effluvium --> History[History]
    Diffuse --> Androgenetic_Alopecia[Androgenetic Alopecia]
    Androgenetic_Alopecia --> Hormone_Levels[Hormone Levels]

    // Findings for Eyebrows
    Eyebrows --> Madarosis[Madarosis]
    Madarosis --> Hypothyroidism[Hypothyroidism]
    Hypothyroidism --> TSH_T4[TSH and T4]
    Madarosis --> Alopecia_Areata_Eyebrows[Alopecia Areata]
    Alopecia_Areata_Eyebrows --> Autoimmune_Markers[Autoimmune Markers]
    Madarosis --> Blepharitis[Blepharitis]
    Blepharitis --> Clinical_Diagnosis[Clinical Diagnosis]

    // Findings for Eyes
    Eyes --> Pallor[Pallor]
    Pallor --> Anemia[Anemia]
    Anemia --> Hemoglobin[Hemoglobin]
    Pallor --> Shock[Shock]
    Shock --> Blood_Pressure[Blood Pressure]
    Eyes --> Jaundice[Jaundice]
    Jaundice --> Liver_Disease[Liver Disease]
    Liver_Disease --> LFTs[Liver Function Tests]
    Jaundice --> Hemolysis[Hemolysis]
    Hemolysis --> Bilirubin[Bilirubin Levels]

 // Findings for Nose
Nose --> Deformities_Nose[Deformities]
Deformities_Nose --> Trauma_Nose[Trauma]
Trauma_Nose --> Imaging_Nose[Imaging (X-ray, CT)]
Deformities_Nose --> Congenital_Nose[Congenital Abnormalities]
Congenital_Nose --> Clinical_Diagnosis_Nose[Clinical Diagnosis]
Deformities_Nose --> Infections_Nose[Infections (e.g., Syphilis)]
Infections_Nose --> Serology_Syphilis[Serology for Syphilis]
Deformities_Nose --> Tumors_Nose[Tumors]
Tumors_Nose --> Biopsy_Nose[Biopsy]

// Findings for Mouth
Mouth --> Hydration_Mouth[Hydration]
Hydration_Mouth --> Dry_Mouth[Dry]
Dry_Mouth --> Dehydration_Mouth[Dehydration]
Dehydration_Mouth --> History_Hydration_Mouth[History of Fluid Intake]
Dry_Mouth --> Mouth_Breathing_Mouth[Mouth Breathing]
Mouth_Breathing_Mouth --> History_Mouth_Breathing[History]
Hydration_Mouth --> Moist_Mouth[Moist]
Moist_Mouth --> Normal_Hydration_Mouth[Normal]

Mouth --> Cyanosis_Mouth[Cyanosis]
Cyanosis_Mouth --> Present_Cyanosis_Mouth[Present]
Present_Cyanosis_Mouth --> Hypoxia_Mouth[Hypoxia]
Hypoxia_Mouth --> Oxygen_Saturation_Mouth[Oxygen Saturation]
Hypoxia_Mouth --> ABG_Mouth[Arterial Blood Gas]

Mouth --> Buccal_Mucosa_Mouth[Buccal Mucosa]
Buccal_Mucosa_Mouth -> Thrush_Mouth[Oral Thrush]
Thrush_Mouth -> Candidiasis_Mouth[Candidiasis]
Candidiasis_Mouth -> Clinical_Diagnosis_Thrush[Clinical Diagnosis]
Candidiasis_Mouth -> Culture_Thrush[Culture if necessary]

Buccal_Mucosa_Mouth -> Ulcers_Mouth[Ulcers]
Ulcers_Mouth -> Aphthous_Mouth[Aphthous Ulcers]
Aphthous_Mouth -> History_Ulcers_Mouth[History]
Ulcers_Mouth -> Herpes_Mouth[Herpes Simplex]
Herpes_Mouth -> Viral_Culture_Mouth[Viral Culture]
Ulcers_Mouth -> Malignancy_Ulcers_Mouth[Malignancy]
Malignancy_Ulcers_Mouth -> Biopsy_Ulcers_Mouth[Biopsy]

Buccal_Mucosa_Mouth -> Scurvy_Mouth[Scurvy]
Scurvy_Mouth -> Vitamin_C_Deficiency_Mouth[Vitamin C Deficiency]
Vitamin_C_Deficiency_Mouth -> Dietary_History_Mouth[Dietary History]
Vitamin_C_Deficiency_Mouth -> Serum_Vitamin_C_Mouth[Serum Vitamin C]

Buccal_Mucosa_Mouth -> Angular_Stomatitis_Mouth[Angular Stomatitis]
Angular_Stomatitis_Mouth -> Vitamin_B_Deficiency_Mouth[Vitamin B Deficiency]
Vitamin_B_Deficiency_Mouth -> Blood_Tests_Vitamins_Mouth[Blood Tests for Vitamins]
Angular_Stomatitis_Mouth -> Iron_Deficiency_Mouth[Iron Deficiency]
Iron_Deficiency_Mouth -> Iron_Studies_Mouth[Iron Studies]
